title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Feb 25 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Feb 25 2022
description:
Biden's incompetence could plunge us into a World War. Buck adds: "What gets everyone so frightened is, is Putin crazy enough to actually go nuclear?" Clay notes that, as messy as Ukraine is, what seems clear is that there is now "an unholy alliance" between Russia and China, who's been spilling U.S. intelligence from Biden, who was trying to get China on board against Russia. Desperate Biden regime schedules SCOTUS announcement on day Kiev is being invaded. Hillary (always good, Buck says, if you are looking for "the Big Lie") fibs about Trump's interview with Clay and Buck. C&B take calls.
